; prj/
;
; This directory contains Lauterbach Trace32 project files (.t32 or .cmm)
; used to configure the debug session for the Aurix TC4xx target.
;
; Project files are referenced via:
;   vFctn_T32_CommandCreate_prj(chCommand, "project_file.cmm")
;
; Add project-specific configuration files here as needed.
